  <title>Gio.Drive.prototype.start</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
function start(flags: Gio.DriveStartFlags, mount_operation: Gio.MountOperation, cancellable: Gio.Cancellable, callback: Gio.AsyncReadyCallback): void {
    // Gjs wrapper for g_drive_start()
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Asynchronously starts a drive.</p>  <p>When the operation is finished, <code>callback</code> will be called.
You can then call <link xref="Gio.start_finish"/> to obtain the
result of the operation.</p>
  <p>Since 2.22</p>
